<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title><%= title %></title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"></head>
<body><div id="cursor"></div><div id="cursor-ring"></div><%- include('../partials/navbar') %><div class="page-hero"><div class="page-hero-bg"></div><div class="grid-bg"></div><div class="page-hero-content"><span class="page-tag">Our Impact</span><h1>Making a <span>Difference</span></h1><p>AURA WASH is committed to environmental sustainability and community impact.</p></div></div><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;"><span class="section-label">Sustainability</span><h2 class="section-title">By the Numbers</h2></div><div style="display;grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:2rem;"><div style="background:rgba(0,85,221,0.06);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2rem;text-align:center;" class="reveal"><div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--cyan);font-family:Orbitron,monospace;">85%</div><p style="color:var(--text);margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.95rem;">Water Recycled</p><p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text);">Our systems recover and recycle water.</p></div><div style="background:rgba(0,85,221,0.06);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2rem;text-align:center;" class="reveal"><div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--cyan);font-family:Orbitron,monospace;">2M+</div><p style="color:var(--text);margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.95rem;">Gallons Saved</p><p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text);">Thanks to smart technology.</p></div><div style="background:rgba(0,85,221,0.06);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2rem;text-align:center;" class="reveal"><div style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--cyan);font-family:Orbitron,monospace;">500+</div><p style="color:var(--text);margin-top:0.5rem;font-size:0.95rem;">Jobs Created</p><p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text);">Across our operating regions.</p></div></div><div style="background:rgba(0,85,221,0.06);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2.5rem;margin-top:2rem;text-align:center;" class="reveal"><h3 style="color:white;margin-bottom:1rem;font-family:Orbitron,monospace;">Community Commitment</h3><p style="color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">AURA WASH believes in giving back. We donate to local charities, support educational programs, and invest in the communities we serve.</p></div></div></section><%- include('../partials/footer') %><script src="/js/main.js"></script></body></html>
